Users: 4300
Branch Network: 10.0.0.0/8

ANSWER:
No. of Bits: /13
Subnet Mask: /32 - /13 = /19
Increment: 32i, 3rd Octet
Sub-network: 10.0.32.0/19
First Usable IP Host: 10.0.32.1/19 (Gateway IP)
Last Usable IP Host: 10.0.63.255/19 (Broadcast IP)
Next Network: 10.0.64.0/19 

